translation[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,53,"Nkosi yethu! Siyakholwa koko Ukutyhilileyo, kwaye silandela uMthunywa (u’Isâ) ke ngoko sibhale ndawonye nabo bangqinayo (okokuba akukho thixo wumbi ngaphandle koAllâh)”"
  3,54,"Baza abangakholwayo baqulunqa iyelenqe lokumbulala u’Isâ, naYe uAllâh Waqulunqa. UAllâh yiNtshatsheli kubaqulunqi"
  3,55,"Kananjalo uAllâh Wathi: “Hini na ‘Isâ! Mna Ndiya kukwenza ufe2, Ndikuhlambulule (kwizityholo) zabo bangakholwayo, Ndenze abo bakulandelayo babe ngentla kunabo bangakholwayo kude kube yiMini yoVuko. Nize nibuyele kuM, Mna Ndigwebe phakathi kwenu mayela noko naniphikisana ngako”"
  3,56,"Ngokuphathelene nabo bangakholwayo, Ndiya kubohlwaya ngesohlwayo esibuhlungu kweli hlabathi nakuBomi oBuzayo yaye abayi kuba nabancedisi”"
  3,57,"Ngokuphathelene nabo bakholwayo, benza imisebenzi yobulungisa, uAllâh Uza kubahlawula umvuzo wabo ngokugcweleyo. Ukanti uAllâh Akabathandi abagabadeli"
  3,58,Oku koko Sikucengceleza kuWe (Muhammad) kuziiVesi neSikhumbuzo sobulumko
  3,59,"Inene, imfano ka’Isâ phambi koAllâh inqwa nemfano ka- Adam. (UAllâh) Wamdala (uAdam) ngothuli, Wathi kuye: “Yibakho!” Wabakho"
  3,60,"(Le) yinyaniso evela eNkosini yakho, ke wena uze ungabi ngomnye wabo bathandabuzayo"
  3,61,"Nabani na ophikisana nawe ngokuphathelene no’Isâ, emveni kokuba ulwazi lufikile kuwe yithi: “Yizani sibize oonyana bethu noonyana benu, abafazi bethu nabafazi benu, thina buqu nani buqu, sithandazeni, sicele (ngokunyanisekileyo) ukuba isiqalekiso sihle phezu kwabo baxokayo”"